CRONTAB

*/3 * * * * /bin/bash /home/ubuntu/SCRIPTS/healthcheck.sh > /dev/null 2>&1

Copy the Scripts to /home/ubuntu/SCRIPTS folder. If folder not available please create it.

Run the below command
sudo chmod a+rw /home/ubuntu/SCRIPTS -R

This scripts will create logs as follows:
health.log=> Every 3 minutes healthcheckup will be done and updates this log 
act.log=> Every 3 seconds this will get updated

Note:Both the script in this folder should be run from /home/ubuntu/SCRIPTS folder in all servers
